專業的英文
音標：[ zhuānyè ]  發音：  
英文翻譯手機版1.(學校學科分類)specialized subject; special field of study; speciality; discipline 短語和例子這個系有四個專業。the department offers four specialities.2.(生產部門的各業務部門) specialized trade or profession; special line 短語和例子銀行向專業方向發展。 banks have developed along specialized lines.; 專業部門 specialized department; 專業隊伍 specialized personnel; professional contingent; 專業公司 specialized corporation; specialized company; 專業管理部門 departments that are in charge of managing enterprises; 專業戶 specialized households; specialized production household; 專業技術職務 professional and technical posts; 專業教育 professional education; 專業經理 professional manager; 專業課 specialized course; 專業批發公司 specialized wholesale corporation; 專業情報中心 special information centre; 專業人員 professional man [staff; personnel]; personnel in a specific field; 專業商店 specialized shop; 專業生產 specialized production; 專業市場 specialized market; 專業術語 technical term; 專業說明書 job specification; 專業學校 vocational school; 專業訓練 specialized training; 專業銀行 specialized bank; 專業知識 professional knowledge; 專業主管 professional management; professional executive; 專業作家 professional writer非專業:    non-professional跨專業:    trans-disciplinary雙專業:    double major特點，專業:    eciality特征，專業:    speciality學科，專業:    fach, das; ..er主題，專業:    subject專業 - 建築:    profession - building專業，職業:    profession專業版:    profession edition; professional edition專業廠:    specialmanufacturer專業的:    pro profe ional; pro professional; profl professional; specialist; specialized ...專業店:    speciality store; specially shop/store專業隊:    professional team專業費:    professional fees專業港:    special-purpose port; specialized port專業戶:    family that produces a special product; specialized household; specialized pro ...專業化:    specialization; professionalization  專業化程度高 have a highly specialized div ...專業級:    expert; wella system professional專業架:    rakc rack mount專業街:    special commercial street專業課:    special disciplines; specialized course專業庫:    career bank專業類:    professional
例句與用法Do you belong to any professional associations ?你是哪個專業學會的？Banks have developed along specialized lines .銀行向專業方向發展。His work lacks that professional touch .他的作品缺乏那種專業修飾。Her voice should be professionally trained .她在運嗓上應接受專業訓練。His field of expertise was steroids .他的專業領域是甾族化合物。The department offers four specialities .這個系有四個專業。Biochemistry is his specialty .生物化學是他的專業（專長）。Teams were formed which had good or bad luck .生死難卜的專業小組組織起來了。You need a professional to sort out your finances .你需要專業人士替你管理財務。Many specialistic techniques contribute to archaeology .許多專業技術對考古學作出貢獻。更多例句：  1  2  3  4  5用"專業"造句  


